ited States presidential election in New York, 1980|1980]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''52.4%''' ''7,174''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|36.6% ''5,010''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|11.0% ''1,506''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1976|1976]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''56.7%''' ''7,659''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|42.5% ''5,745''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.8% ''104''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1972|1972]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''67.7%''' ''9,368''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|32.1% ''4,441''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.2% ''33''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1968|1968]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''54.5%''' ''7,083''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|40.2% ''5,222''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|5.4% ''700''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1964|1964]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|33.4% ''4,473''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''66.5%''' ''8,890''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.1% ''13''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in New York, 1960|1960]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''60.6%''' ''8,741''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democr