oah Garcia\n|-\n| rowspan=9 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2005'''<br /><small>(29th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Robin Padilla]]''' \n| '''''[[La Visa Loca]]'''''\n| '''Jeff Huson'''\n|-\n| [[Carlo Aquino]] \n| ''Sa Aking Pagkagising Mula sa Kamulatan''\n| Rey\n|-\n| [[Dennis Trillo]] \n| ''[[Blue Moon (2006 film)|Blue Moon]]''\n| Kyle Pineda\n|-\n| Jaime Wilson \n| ''Big Time''\n| Wilson\n|-\n| [[Nathan Lopez]] \n| ''[[The Blossoming of Maximo Oliveros|Ang Pagdadalaga ni Maximo Oliveros]]''\n| Maximo Oliveros\n|-\n| Rhenuel Ordo\u00f1o \n| ''Ang Daan Patungong Kalimugtong''\n| \n|-\n| [[Ricky Davao]]\n| ''Pusang Gala''\n| Boyet\n|-\n| [[Yul Servo]] \n| ''Ilusyon''\n| Miguel\n|-\n| rowspan=8 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2006'''<br /><small>(30th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Mark Gil]]'''\n| '''''Rotonda'''''\n| \n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Rustom Padilla]]''' \n| '''''[[Zsa Zsa Zaturnnah]]'''''\n| '''Ada'''\n|- \n| Alchris Galura \n| ''Batad: Sa Paang Palay''\n| Ag-ap\n|- \n| [[Jett Pangan]] \n| ''[[Tulad ng Dati (film)|Tulad ng Dati]]''\n| Jett Pangan\n|- \n| Mario Magallano \n| ''Rekados''\n| James\n|- \n| [[Ryan Agoncillo]] \n| ''[[Kasal, Kasali, Kasalo]]''\n| Jerome/Jed\n|- \n| [[Sid Lucero]] \n| '' [[Donsol (film)|Donsol]]''\n| Daniel\n|-\n| rowspan=9 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2007'''<br /><small>(31st)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Jason Abalos]]''' \n| '''''Endo'''''\n| '''Leo'''\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Sid Lucero]]'''\n| '''''Selda'''''\n| '''Rommel'''\n|- \n| [[Jerrold Tarog]]\n| ''[[Confessional (film)|Confessional]]''\n| Ryan Pastor\n|- \n| Roeder Camanag \n| ''Death in the Land of Encantos''\n| Benjamin Agusan\n|- \n| [[Jinggoy Estrada]]\n| ''Katas ng Saudi''\n| Oca\n|- \n| [[Jiro Manio]]\n| ''Tambolista''\n| Jason\n|- \n| [[Romnick Sarmenta]]\n| ''Prinsesa''\n| \n|- \n| Shielbert Manuel\n| ''[[Tribu (film)|Tribu]]''\n| Makoy/Sacred Brown Tribe\n|-\n|