th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Sid Lucero]]'''\n| '''''[[Muli (film)|Muli]]'''''\n| '''Jun Bernabe'''\n|-\n| [[John Arcilla]]\n| ''Halaw''\n| \n|-\n| Perry Dizon\n| ''Sheika''\n| Gary\n|-\n| [[Ronnie Lazaro]]\n| ''Ishmael''\n| Ishmael\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[Noy (film)|Noy]]''\n| Manolo \"Noy\" Agapito\n|-\n| [[Pen Medina]] \n| ''Layang Bilanggo''\n| Paul\n|-\n| [[Sam Milby]] \n| ''Third World Happy''\n| Wesley\n|-\n| Fanny Serrano \n| ''Tarima''\n| Roselo\n|-\n| [[Joel Torre]] \n| ''[[Amigo (film)|Amigo]]''\n| Rafael\n|-\n| rowspan=12 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[35th Gawad Urian Awards|2011]]'''<br /><small>(35th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Paulo Avelino]]'''\n| '''''Ang Sayaw ng Dalawang Kaliwang Paa'''''\n| '''Marlon'''\n|-\n| Bong Cabrera\n| ''Sa Ilalim ng Tulay''\n| Nono\n|-\n| [[Tirso Cruz III]]\n| ''Bisperas''\n| \n|-\n| [[Alfred Vargas]]\n| ''Teoriya''\n| \n|-\n| [[Ronnie Lazaro]]\n| ''Boundary''\n| \n|-\n| [[Raymond Bagatsing]]\n| ''Boundary''\n| \n|-\n| [[TJ Trinidad]]\n| ''Deadline: The Reign of Impunity''\n| Ross Rivera\n|-\n| [[Martin Escudero]]\n| ''Zombadings 1: Patayin sa Shokot si Remington''\n| Remington\n|-\n| [[JM de Guzman]]\n| ''[[The Woman in the Septic Tank|Ang Babae sa Septic Tank]]''\n| Bingbong\n|-\n| [[Kean Cipriano]]\n| ''[[The Woman in the Septic Tank|Ang Babae sa Septic Tank]]''\n| Rainier de la Cuesta\n|-\n| Jess Mendoza\n| ''The Natural Phenomenon of Madness''\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=14 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[36th Gawad Urian Awards|2012]]'''<br /><small>(36th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Jericho Rosales]]'''\n| '''''[[Alagwa (film)|Alagwa]]'''''\n| '''Robert Lim'''\n|-\n| [[JM de Guzman]]\n| ''Intoy Syokoy ng Kalye Marino''\n| \n|-\n| Nico Antonio\n| ''Posas''\n| \n|-\n| Kristoffer King\n| ''Oros''\n| \n|-\n| [[Dominic Roco]]\n| ''[[Ang Nawawala]]''\n| Gibson Bonifacio\n|-\n| [[Eddie Garcia]]\n| ''[[Bwakaw]]''\n| Rene\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[S