o\n|-\n| [[Johnny Delgado]] \n| ''Salome''\n| Macario\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1982'''<br /><small>(7th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Phillip Salvador]]'''\n| '''''Cain at Abel'''''\n| '''Lorenzo'''\n|-\n| [[Mark Gil]]\n| ''[[Batch '81]]''\n| Sid Lucero\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Cain at Abel''\n| Ellis\n|-\n| [[Vic Vargas]]\n| ''In This Corner''\n| Flash Gonzaga\n|-\n| [[Joel Torre]]\n| ''[[Oro, Plata, Mata]]''\n| Miguel Lorenzo\n|-\n| rowspan=3 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1983'''<br /><small>(8th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Phillip Salvador]]'''\n| '''''[[Of the Flesh|Karnal]]'''''\n| '''Narcing'''\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Broken Marriage''\n| Rene\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1984'''<br /><small>(9th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Jay Ilagan]]''' \n| ''Sister Stella L.''\n| '''Nick Fajardo'''\n|-\n| [[Phillip Salvador]]\n| ''Baby Tsina''\n| Roy\n|-\n| [[Ronnie Lazaro]]\n| ''Boatman'''\n| Felipe\n|-\n| [[Tommy Abuel]]\n| ''Bukas May Pangarap''\n| Udong\n|-\n| [[Jay Ilagan]]\n| ''Soltero'''\n| Crispin Rodriguez\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1985'''<br /><small>(10th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Phillip Salvador]]'''\n| '''''[[This Is My Country (film)|Bayan ko: Kapit sa Patalim]]'''''\n| '''Turing'''\n|- \n| [[Tommy Abuel]]\n| ''Bakit Manipis ang Ulap''\n| \n|-\n| [[Ace Vergel]]\n| ''Bomba Arienda''\n| Roger \"Bomba\" Arienda\n|-\n| [[Eddie Garcia]]\n| ''Miguelito: Batang Rebelde''\n| Ven Herrera\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''Miguelito: Batang Rebelde''\n| Miguelito/Mike\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1986'''<br /><small>(11th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Michael de Mesa]]'''\n| '''''Unfaithful Wife'''''\n| '''Crispin'''\n|- \n| [[Dan Alvaro]]\n| ''Bagong Hari''\n| \n|-\n| [[Gino Antonio]]\n| ''Takaw Tukso''\n| \n|-\n| [[Julio Diaz (actor)|Julio Diaz]]\n| ''