riel'''\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''Akin Ka Magdusa Man Ako''\n| \n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Ipagpatawad Mo''\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1992'''<br /><small>(16th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Gabby Concepcion]]'''\n| '''''Narito ang Puso Ko'''''\n| \n|-\n| [[Julio Diaz (actor)|Julio Diaz]]\n| ''Bayani''\n| Carol\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]] \n| ''Bakit Labis Kitang Mahal''\n| Tommy\n|-\n| [[Richard Gomez]]\n| ''Ikaw ang Lahat sa Akin''\n| Cesar\n|-\n| [[Ricky Davao]]\n| ''Apoy sa Puso''\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=5 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1993'''<br /><small>(17th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Richard Gomez]]'''\n| '''''Saan Ka Man Naroon'''''\n| '''Miguel'''\n|-\n| [[Cesar Montano]]\n| ''Leonardo delos Reyes: Alyas Waway''\n| Leonardo delos Reyes/Nards\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Gaano Kita Kamahal''\n| \n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''[[May Minamahal (film)|May MInamahal]]''\n| Carlitos\n|-\n| rowspan=4 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1994'''<br /><small>(18th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Richard Gomez]]'''\n| '''''Wating'''''\n| '''Ardo'''\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Bakit Ngayon Ka LAng''\n| Fatimah Buen\n|-\n| [[Phillip Salvador]]\n| ''Ka Hector''\n| Ka Hector/Che/Poldo\n|-\n| rowspan=5 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''1995'''<br /><small>(19th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Aga Muhlach]]'''\n| '''''[[Sana Maulit Muli (film)|Sana Maulit Muli]]'''''\n| '''Jerry'''\n|-\n| [[Richard Gomez]]\n| ''Dahas''\n| Jake\n|-\n| [[Jao Mapa]]\n| ''Pare Ko''\n| Chipper\n|-\n| [[Jomari Yllana]]\n| ''Pare Ko''\n| Mackie\n|-\n| rowspan=5 style=\"text-align:center\" |  '''1996'''<br /><small>(20th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Tonton Gutierrez]]'''\n| '''''Abot Kamay ang Pangarap'''''\n| '''Roy'''\n|- \n| [[Eddie Garcia]]\n| ''[[Bakit May Kahapon Pa?]]''\n| Gen. Valderama\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''[[Madrasta]]''\n| Edward\n|-\n|