el\n|- \n| [[Diether Ocampo]]\n| ''La Vida Rosa''\n| Dado\n|-\n| [[Mark Anthony Fernandez]]\n| ''Dos Ekis''\n| Benito\n|-\n| Paolo Rivero\n| ''[[Live Show (film)|Live Show]]''\n| Rolly\n|-\n| [[Ricky Davao]]\n| ''Minsan May Isang Puso''\n| Simon Pacheco\n|-\n| rowspan=9 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2002'''<br /><small>(26th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Jay Manalo]]'''\n| '''''Prosti'''''\n| '''Nonoy Laki'''\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''[[Kailangan Kita]]''\n| Carl Diesta\n|-\n| [[Albert Martinez]]\n| ''Laman''\n| Omar\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| [[Dekada '70 (film)|Dekada '70]]\n| Juli\u00e1n Bartolome, Sr.\n|-\n| [[Ricky Davao]]\n| ''[[American Adobo]]''\n| Gerry\n|-\n| [[Rudy Fernandez (actor)|Rudy Fernandez]]\n| ''Diskarte''\n| Jake\n|-\n| [[Vhong Navarro]]\n| ''[[Jologs]]''\n| Kulas\n|-\n| [[Yul Servo]]\n| ''Laman''\n| Dodong\n|-\n| rowspan=5 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2003'''<br /><small>(27th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Jiro Manio]]'''\n| '''''[[Magnifico (film)|Magnifico]]'''''\n| '''Magnifico'''\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]] \n| ''Kung Ako na Lang Sana''\n| Vince/Enteng\n|-\n| [[Cogie Domingo]]\n| ''Anghel sa Lupa''\n| Benjo\n|-\n| Kristoffer King\n| ''[[Woman of Breakwater|Babae sa Breakwater]]''\n| Basilio\n|-\n| rowspan=7 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2004'''<br /><small>(28th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Cesar Montano]]'''\n| '''''[[Panaghoy sa Suba]]'''''\n| '''Duroy'''\n|-\n| [[Jomari Yllana]] \n| ''[[Minsan Pa]]''\n| Jerry\n|-\n| [[Pen Medina]]\n| ''Ebolusyon ng Isang Pamilyang Pilipino''\n| Kadyo\n|-\n| [[Piolo Pascual]] \n| ''[[Milan (2004 film)|Milan]]''\n| Lino\n|-\n| [[Ronnie Lazaro]]\n| ''Ebolusyon ng Isang Pamilyang Pilipino''\n| Fernando\n|-\n| [[Yul Servo]] \n| ''[[Naglalayag]]''\n| Noah Garcia\n|-\n| rowspan=9 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2005'''<br /><small>(29th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Robin Padilla]]''' \n| '''''[[La Visa Loca]]'''''\n