|- \n| [[Baron Geisler]]\n| ''Jay''\n| Jay Santiago\n|- \n| Julian Duque \n| ''Boses''\n| Onyok\n|- \n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[Daybreak (2008 film)|Daybreak]]''\n| JP\n|- \n| Paolo Rivero \n| ''[[Daybreak (2008 film)|Daybreak]]''\n| William\n|- \n| Timothy Mabalot \n| ''Brutus, Ang Paglalakbay''\n| Adag\n|- \n| Perry Dizon \n| ''[[Melancholia (2008 film)|Melancholia]]'' \n| Julian Tomas/Pimp\n|- \n| [[Neil Ryan Sese]]\n| ''Huling Pasada''\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=11 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2009'''<br /><small>(33rd)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Lou Veloso]]'''\n| '''''Colorum'''''\n| '''Pedro Trinidad'''\n|-\n| Raul Arellano\n| ''Himpapawid''\n| \n|-\n| [[Allen Dizon]]\n| ''Dukot ''\n| \n|-\n| Dwight Gaston \n| ''The Arrival''\n| \n|-\n| [[John Lloyd Cruz]]\n| ''[[In My Life (2009 film)|In My Life]]''\n| Noel Villanueva\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[Kinatay]]''\n| Peping\n|-\n| Joey Paras\n| ''Last Supper No. 3''\n| Wilson Na\u00f1awa\n|-\n| [[Felix Roco]]\n| ''Engkwentro''\n| \n|-\n| [[Alfred Vargas]]\n| ''Colorum''\n| Simon Madriga\n|-\n| Jacky Woo\n| ''Walang Hanggang Paalam''\n| Yoshi Imaizumi\n|-\n|}\n\n===2010s===\n[[File:John Lloyd Cruz at ABS-CBN Talent Center, May 2010.jpg|thumb|100px|[[John Lloyd Cruz]] was nominated for Gawad Urian Best Actor in 2010. He won Best Actor in 2015]]\n[[File:Sam Milby by Ronn Tan, April 2010.png|thumb|100px|[[Sam Milby]] was nominated for Gawad Urian Best Actor in 2011]]\n[[File:Ananda Everingham.jpg|thumb|100px|[[Ananda Everingham]] was nominated for Gawad Urian Best Actor in 2013]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#ABCDEF\"\n! width=\"8%\" | Year\n! width=\"19%\" | Actor\n! width=\"19%\" | Film\n! width=\"19%\" | Role\n|-\n| rowspan=10 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2010'''<br /><small>(34th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#ABCDEF\"\n| '''[[Sid Lucero]]'''\n| '''''[[Muli (film)|Muli]]'''''\n| '''Jun Bernabe'''\n|-\n| [[John Arcilla]]\n| ''Halaw''\n| \n|-\n| Perry Dizon\n| '