or)|C\u00e9sar Ram\u00edrez]]\n| ''Huwag Mo Akong Limutin''\n| Arturo\n|-\n| [[Fernando Poe Jr.]]\n| ''Walang Daigdig''\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[10th FAMAS Awards|1961]]'''<br /><small>(10th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Leopoldo Salcedo]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''[[The Moises Padilla Story]]'''''\n| '''Moises Padilla'''\n|-\n| [[Efren Reyes Sr.]]\n| ''Alaala Kita''\n|\n|-\n| [[Eddie del Mar]]\n| ''Noli Me Tangere''\n| Crisostomo Ibarra\n|-\n| Ronald Remy\n| ''Pusong Bakal''\n| Esteban\n|-\n| [[Nestor De Villa]]\n| ''Mga Yapak na Walang Bakas''\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=9 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[11th FAMAS Awards|1962]]'''<br /><small>(11th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Joseph Estrada]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Markang Rehas'''''\n|\n|-\n| [[Fernando Poe Jr.]]\n| ''Ako ang Katarungan''\n|\n|-\n| [[Berting Labra]]\n| ''Ano ba Choy''\n|\n|-\n| [[Pancho Magalona]]\n| ''El Filibusterismo''\n| Simoun\n|-\n| [[Romeo Vasquez (actor)|Romeo Vasquez]]\n| ''Pitong Kabanalan ng Isang Makasalanan''\n|\n|-\n| [[Eddie del Mar]]\n| ''Sino ang Matapang''\n|\n|-\n| [[C\u00e9sar Ram\u00edrez (actor)|C\u00e9sar Ram\u00edrez]]\n| ''Suicide Susy''\n|\n|-\n| [[Fernando Poe Jr.]]\n| ''Walang Pagkalupig''\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=11 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[12th FAMAS Awards|1963]]'''<br /><small>(12th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Eddie Rodriguez]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Sapagkat Kami'y Tao Lamang'''''\n|\n|-\n| [[Van de Leon]]\n| ''3 Mukha ni Pandora''\n|\n|-\n| [[Joseph Estrada]]\n| ''Ito ang Maynila''\n|\n|-\n| Fred Montilla\n| ''The Arsenio Lacson Story''\n| [[Arsenio Lacson]]\n|-\n| [[Nestor de Villa]]\n| ''Naku... Yabang!''\n| \n|-\n| [[Robert Arevalo]]\n| rowspan=2|''Sa Atin ang Daigdig''\n|\n|-\n| [[Eddie Mesa]]\n|\n|-\n| [[Fernando Poe Jr.]] \n| ''Sigaw ng Digmaan''\n|\n|-\n| Juancho Gutierez \n| ''Tres Kantos''\n|\n|-\n| [[G