iyam na Buhay]]''\n| Cedrick\n|-\n| [[Dingdong Dantes]]\n| ''[[She's the One (2013 film)|She's The One]]''\n| Wacky\n|-\n| rowspan=12 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[2015 FAMAS Awards|2014]]'''<br /><small>(63rd)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/entertainment/news/106456-full-list-winners-famas-awards-2015|title=FULL LIST: Winners, FAMAS Awards 2015|publisher=[[Rappler]]|work= |accessdate= December 2, 2015|date=September 21, 2015}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\n| '''[[Allen Dizon]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''[[Magkakabaung]]'''''\n| '''Randy'''\n|-\n| [[Jake Vargas]]\n| ''Asintado''\n| Tonio\n|-\n| [[Robin Padilla]]\n| ''[[Bonifacio: Ang Unang Pangulo]]''\n| [[Andres Bonifacio]]\n|-\n| [[Derek Ramsay]]\n| ''[[English Only, Please]]''\n| Julian Parker\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[Feng Shui 2]]''\n| Lester A\u00f1onuevo\n|-\n| [[Rocco Nacino]]\n| ''[[Hustisya]]''\n| Atty. Gerald\n|-\n| [[Allen Dizon]]\n| ''Kamkam''\n| Johnny\n|-\n| [[E.R. Ejercito]]\n| ''Magnum Muslim .357''\n| Lt. Jamal\n|-\n| [[Daniel Padilla]]\n| ''[[She's Dating the Gangster]]''\n| Kenji Delos Reyes / Kenneth Delos Reyes\n|-\n| [[Piolo Pascual]]\n| ''[[Starting over Again (2014 film)|Starting Over Again]]''\n| Marco Antonio Villanueva III\n|- \n| [[John Lloyd Cruz]]\n| ''[[The Trial (2014 film)|The Trial]]''\n| Ronald Jimenez Jr.\n|-\n| rowspan=11 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[2016 FAMAS Awards|2015]]'''<br /><small>(64th)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/entertainment/news/154473-full-list-famas-awards-2016-winners|title=FULL LIST: Winners, FAMAS Awards 2016|publisher=[[Rappler]]|work= |accessdate= December 4, 2016|date=December 4, 2016}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\n| '''[[Dennis Trillo]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''[[Felix Manalo (film)|Felix Manalo]]'''''\n| '''[[Felix Y. Manalo]]'''\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[You're My Boss]]''\n| Pong Dalupan\n|-\n| [[Daniel Padilla]]\n| ''[[Crazy Beautiful You]