ard winner}}\n| '''''Isang Ama, Dalawang Ina'''''\n| \n|-\n| [[Dolphy]]\n| ''Ang Tatay kong Nanay''\n| Dioscoro Derecho / Coring \n|-\n| [[Rudy Fernandez (actor)|Rudy Fernandez]]\n| ''Anak sa Una, Kasal sa Ina''\n| \n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Lagi na Lamang ba Akong Babae?''\n| Desto\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[28th FAMAS Awards|1979]]'''<br /><small>(28th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Fernando Poe Jr.]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Durugin si Totoy Bato'''''\n| '''Totoy Bato'''\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Ang Alamat ni Julian Makabayan''\n| Julian Makabayan\n|-\n| [[Anthony Alonzo]]\n| ''Dakpin si Junior Bumbay''\n| Junior Bumbay\n|-\n| Ernie Garcia\n| ''Pagmamahal mo Buhay Ko''\n| \n|-\n| [[Rudy Fernandez (actor)|Rudy Fernandez]]\n| ''Star''\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[29th FAMAS Awards|1980]]'''<br /><small>(29th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''Dindo Fernando'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Langis at Tubig'''''\n| '''Bobby Jarlego'''\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''[[Aguila (film)|Aguila]]''\n| Mari\n|-\n| [[Joseph Estrada]]\n| '''Hoy, Tukso Layuan mo Ako''\n| \n|-\n| [[Jay Ilagan]]\n| ''Brutal''\n| Tato\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Taga sa Panahon''\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=8 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[30th FAMAS Awards|1981]]'''<br /><small>(30th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Joseph Estrada]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Kumander Alibasbas'''''\n| '''Cesario Manarang / Kumander Alibasbas'''\n|-\n| [[Fernando Poe Jr.]]\n| ''Ang Maestro''\n|  Hernan de Zuniga\n|-\n| [[Anthony Alonzo]]\n| ''Hulihin si Pepeng Magtanggol''\n| Pepeng Magtanggol\n|-\n| [[Christopher de Leon]]\n| ''Pakawalan Mo Ako''\n| Freddie\n|-\n| [[Vic Silayan]]\n| ''[[Kisapmata]]''\n| Sgt. Diosdado Carandang\n|-\n| [[Rudy Fernandez (actor)|Rudy Fernandez]]\n| ''Pepeng Shotgun''\n| Pepe Medrano\n|-\n| [[Dolphy]]\n| ''