rada]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Katas Ng Saudi'''''\n| '''Oca'''\n|-\n| [[Piolo Pascual]]\n| ''[[Paano Kita Iibigin]]''\n| Lance Monteagundo\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''[[A Love Story (2007 film)|A Love Story]]''\n| Ian Montes\n|-\n| [[John Lloyd Cruz]]\n| ''[[One More Chance (2007 film)|One More Chance]]''\n| Popoy\n|-\n| [[Bong Revilla]]\n| ''[[Resiklo]]''\n| Commander Crisval Sarmiento\n|-\n| rowspan=7 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2008'''<br /><small>(57th)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Allen Dizon]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Paupahan'''''\n| '''Tonio Torres'''\n|-\n| [[Jericho Rosales]]\n| ''[[Baler (film)|Baler]]''\n| Celso Resureccion\n|-\n| [[John Estrada]]\n| ''[[Caregiver (film)|Caregiver]]''\n| Theodore \"Teddy\" Gonzales\n|-\n| [[Richard Gutierrez]]\n| ''[[For the First Time (2008 film)|For The First Time]]''\n| Seth Alexander Villaraza\n|-\n| [[Polo Ravales]]\n| ''Walang Kawala''\n| Joaquin\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''[[When Love Begins]]''\n| Benedicto \"Ben\" Caballero\n|-\n| rowspan=8 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[58th FAMAS Awards|2009]]'''<br /><small>(58th)<ref name=2010famasimdb>{{cite web |url= https://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000232/2010|title=FAMAS Awards for 2009|author=|year= 2011|work= |publisher= IMDb.com|accessdate=}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[Allen Dizon]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''Dukot'''''\n| '''Junix Etrata'''\n|-\n| [[Bong Revilla|Ramon \"Bong\" Revilla]]\n| ''[[Ang Panday (2009 film)|Ang Panday]]''\n| Flavio\n|-\n| [[Gabby Concepcion]]\n| ''[[I Love You, Goodbye (film)|I Love You, Goodbye]]''\n| Dr. Adrian Benitez\n|-\n| [[John Lloyd Cruz]]\n| ''[[In My Life (2009 film)|In My Life]]''\n| Noel Villanueva\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[Kinatay]]''\n| Peping\n|-\n| [[Piolo Pascual]]\n| ''[[Love Me Again (film)|Love Me Again (Land Down Under)]]''\n| Migo\n|-\n| [[John Lloyd Cruz]]\n| ''[[You Changed My Life]]''\n| Miguel \"Miggy\" Montenegro\n|-\n| rowspan=7 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[59th FAMAS Awards|2010]]'''<br /><small>(59th)<ref name=2011famasimdb>{{cite web |url= https://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000232/2011|title=FAMAS Awards for 2010|author=|year= 2011|work= |publisher= IMDb.com|accessdate=}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[John Lloyd Cruz]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''[[Miss You like Crazy (film)|Miss You like Crazy]]'''''\n| '''Allan Alvarez'''\n|-\n| [[Coco Martin]]\n| ''[[Noy (film)|Noy]]''\n| Manolo \"Noy\" Agapito\n|-\n| [[Dennis Trillo]]\n| ''[[Rosario (2010 film)|Rosario]]''\n| Alberto Fernandez\n|-\n| [[Bong Revilla]]\n| rowspan=2|''[[Si Agimat at si Enteng Kabisote]]''\n| Agimat\n|-\n| [[Vic Sotto]]\n| Enteng Kabisote\n|-\n| [[Tirso Cruz III]]\n| ''Sigwa''\n| Oliver\n|-\n| rowspan=8 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[60th FAMAS Awards|2011]]'''<br /><small>(60th)<ref name=2012famasimdb>{{cite web |url= https://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000232/2012|title=FAMAS Awards for 2011|author=|year= 2012|work= |publisher= IMDb.com|accessdate=}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[ER Ejercito]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''[[Manila Kingpin: The Asiong Salonga Story]]'''''\n| '''Nicasio \"Asiong\" Salonga'''\n|-\n| Noni Buencamino\n| ''[[A Mother's Story]]''\n| Gerry Santos\n|-\n| [[Bong Revilla|Ramon 'Bong' Revilla Jr.]]\n| ''[[Ang Panday 2]]''\n| Flavio\n|-\n| [[Aga Muhlach]]\n| ''[[In the Name of Love (2011 film)|In the Name of Love]]''\n| Emman Toledo/Garry Fernandez\n|-\n| [[Derek Ramsay]]\n| ''[[No Other Woman]]''\n| Ram Escaler\n|-\n| [[Dingdong Dantes]]\n| ''[[Segunda Mano]]''\n| Ivan\n|-\n| [[TJ Trinidad]]\n| ''[[The Road (2011 film)|The Road]]''\n| Luis\n|-\n| rowspan=9 style=\"text-align:center\" | '''[[61st FAMAS Awards|2012]]'''<br /><small>(61st)</small>\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86\"\n| '''[[ER Ejercito]]'''{{double dagger|alt=Award winner}}\n| '''''[[El Presidente (film)|El Presidente]]'''''